eriod within\na few $Gyr$ But in the case of $5M_J$ oscillation modes excited in the star are\nmore important.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Dec 2005 21:27:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
