nt agreement, thus providing strong empirical evidence in favor of the\nvalidity of the heuristic formula.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Dec 2005 09:58:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Mar 2006 10:49:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 13 Jul 2006 14:46:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
